observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Management:
Adopt an effective and efficient collection system;
Intensify tax collection campaign through sending follow-up letters/notices of tax collection to delinquent taxpayers to remind them of their tax obligations;
Coordinate/make representations with Punong Barangays and seek their assistance for them (barangay officials) to personally deliver the above notices/letters to concerned individuals in the locality and then personally advise/oblige them to settle their accounts; and
Efficient and effective collection must be observed specifically to Dinapigue Mining Corporation as the biggest delinquent real property taxpayer.

